        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. Entada simplicata. A. Leaf with 1 pair of pinnae (only one represented), each one with two 2 pairs of leaflets. B. Leaf with 3 pairs of pinnae (only one represented), each ones with 3 pairs of leaflets. C. Detail of a raceme, with two floral buds illustrated. D. Flower. E. Fruit (st: stipe). A from Pessoni 639 (UFRR); B–D from Pessoni 574 (UFRR); E from Flores & Peixoto 2147 (MIRR). Drawn by R.S. Rodrigues." ;
